data.description: Welcome to 14806 SE Bush St, a beautifully appointed residence in outer SE Portland at the base of Powell Butte. This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, spanning 2,276 sq ft on a generous 6,100 sq ft corner lot, offers the perfect blend of modern living and classic charm. The heart of this home is its exquisite kitchen, where quartz counters meet a stylish tile backsplash, complemented by stainless steel appliances including a stove with double ovens and a convenient built-in microwave. The Shaker style cabinets provide ample storage and a touch of sophistication. The main level has 2 bedrooms and full bath, it has gleaming wood floors, adding warmth and character to the living spaces. Both bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated, showcasing modern fixtures and elegant finishes. The lower level of this home offers versatility and functionality. A comfortable family room provides the perfect space for relaxation, while a dedicated laundry room adds convenience to your daily routine. Additionally, there are two bonus rooms, ideal for a home office, gym, or playroom ? the possibilities are endless. The upper floor boasts 2 large bedrooms and a full bath. This property comes complete with an oversized detached garage, offering plenty of space for vehicles and additional storage. The large corner lot provides ample room for outdoor activities and gardening. RV owners will appreciate the dedicated parking and storage space, making it convenient for adventures on the road. Nestled in a vibrant neighborhood, this home enjoys the best of both worlds a tranquil residential setting while being conveniently close to local amenities, schools, parks, and shopping centers. Easy access to major highways ensures a seamless commute. [Home Energy Score = 4. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10008606]
